%%%
FAQ-GEN-Q03
%%
If you are having problems
%%
MiniVend is not guaranteed to be supported in any fashion other
than to make full source code of the current version available. However,
the author is interested in making MiniVend as reliable and troublefree
as possible.  Forward bug reports, questions and comments to Mike
Heins,&lt;mikeh<STRONG>@iac</STRONG>.net&gt;.

The official MiniVend web site is:

<PRE>   <A HREF="http://www.iac.net/~mikeh/mvend.html">http://www.iac.net/~mikeh/mvend.html</A>
</PRE>

The latest version of the software, this FAQ, and the current bug list,
are available there.  Your problem may not be unique -- check the site
first.

See the next section for troubles with running MiniVend on ISP
sites.

MiniVend is intended to work on Perl Version 5.001m and higher, but
the author does not have the resources (read time) to regression
